This concludes our ECG learning modules! We hope that we provided a foundation for ECG
interpretation that you can continue to develop throughout your training. We also hope you
learned a little physiology and management along the way. If you have any feedback,
comments, questions, or suggestions please reach out. We wish you the best of luck throughout
your medical training and future career.
